  "notes": [
    "This study represents the first comparative genomic analysis of hepatocellular carcinoma between chimpanzees and humans",
    "The high frequency of TSC2 mutations in chimpanzee HCC (80%) versus human HCC (7%) suggests species-specific oncogenic pathways",
    "Despite higher mutation burden in chimpanzees, humans show stronger positive selection pressure in HCC genomes"
  ]
